                  <interp inst="t18280529-175-crimeloc971" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280529-175-off968 t18280529-175-crimeloc971"></join>. On the 18th of May I saw the prisoner come to our window, press his hand against a blacking paper, which was pasted in the window; he put his hand through the paper, took our four gilt seals and ran away - I pursued and took him about one hundred yards off; he threw them down just before I got up; I picked them up, seized him, and gave him in charge.</p>
